de.htwg_konstanz.ebus.framework.wholesaler.api.boa
Class CountryBOA

java.lang.Object
  de.htwg_konstanz.ebus.framework.wholesaler.api.boa.CountryBOA

public class CountryBOA
extends java.lang.Object

The CountryBOA provides common CRUD operations (Create Read Update Delete) for the country entity.

The business object BOCountry represents a country entity with it's common attributes like name, isoCode or currency.

The following example code shows how to create and persist a new country entity using the CountryBOA. 

 // load a existing currency
 BOCurrency currency = CurrencyBOA.getInstance().findCurrency(TEST_COUNTRY_CURRENCY_CODE);
 if (currency != null)
 {              
        // create the country
        BOCountry country = new BOCountry();
        country.setIsocode(TEST_COUNTRY_ISOCODE);
        country.setName(TEST_COUNTRY_NAME);
        country.setCurrency(currency);
        CountryBOA.getInstance().saveOrUpdate(country);
 }
The following example code shows how to load an existing country entity, using the CountryBOA. 
 // load the country
 BOCountry country = CountryBOA.getInstance().findCountry(TEST_COUNTRY_ISOCODE);
The following example code shows how to load and update an existing country entity, using the CountryBOA. 
 // load the country
 BOCountry country = CountryBOA.getInstance().findCountry(TEST_COUNTRY_ISOCODE);
 if (country != null)
 {              
        // change the country name 
        country.setName(TEST_COUNTRY_UPDATED_NAME);
        CountryBOA.getInstance().saveOrUpdate(country);
 }
The following example code shows how to delete an existing country entity, using the CountryBOA. 
 // load the country
 BOCountry country = CountryBOA.getInstance().findCountry(TEST_COUNTRY_ISOCODE);
 if (country != null)
 {              
        // delete the country
        CountryBOA.getInstance().delete(country);
 }
